		<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; margin: 6.0pt 0cm 6.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: 'Verdana','sans-serif'; color: #645d53;">Principe d&rsquo;interdiction et autorisations sp&eacute;ciales</span></p>
